OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FITV News Political Editor Robert
OL,7,FPeston spoke to a group of voters in
OL,8,FMakerfield to find out what they
OL,9,Freally thought ahead of one of the
OL,10,Fcountry's most consequential
OL,11,Fbyelections
OL,13,FWords by ITV News Producer Kieran
OL,14,FCarter
OL,16,FThe voters of Makerfield will soon
OL,17,Fhead to the polls to vote in what has
OL,18,Fbeen described as one of the UK's most
OL,19,Fconsequential byelections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
