OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FPolls have consistently predicted it
OL,7,Fwill be a race between Labour and
OL,8,FReform UK, with the result of the vote
OL,9,Fon June 18 potentially paving the way
OL,10,Ffor the Mayor of Greater Manchester,
OL,11,FAndy Burnham, to challenge the prime
OL,12,Fminister in a future leadership race.
OL,14,FWith an increased focus on Makerfield,
OL,15,Fcommentators have joked that its
OL,16,Fpopulation have all been voxed at
OL,17,Fleast twice over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
