OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FBut away from the barrage of political
OL,7,Fthink pieces, what do they really
OL,8,Fthink about the current occupant of
OL,9,FNumber 10 Downing Street, the man
OL,10,Fhoping to replace him, and the plumber
OL,11,Fseeking to send him back to the
OL,12,FManchester mayoralty with his tail
OL,13,Fbetween his legs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
