OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FEven those speaking to ITV News who
OL,7,Fbacked Labour and had positive things
OL,8,Fto say about the prime minister felt
OL,9,Fhe was the wrong man to lead the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,F"I've got a lot of time for Keir
OL,13,FStarmer on the basis that I think he's
OL,14,Fan honourable man," said Kieran, who
OL,15,Fworks in a call centre in Wigan and
OL,16,Fvotes Labour.
OL,18,F"I just don't necessarily think he's
OL,19,Fthe right man for the role he's in."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
