PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FOlivia, who works as a secretary, said
OL,7,Fthat for her, it came down to the PM's
OL,8,Flack of conviction.
OL,10,F"I think a lot of the criticisms of
OL,11,Fthe Labour Party have been down to
OL,12,FKeir Starmer's sort of lack of, well,
OL,13,Fanything. He doesn't really seem to
OL,14,Fstand his ground on anything at all."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
