OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FPointing to why the Labour candidate
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has been so talked up as
OL,8,Fa potential Labour leader, Olivia
OL,9,Fcontinued: "I think having someone in
OL,10,Fpower who speaks with conviction and,
OL,11,Fyou know, stands for what they stand
OL,12,Ffor, I think that would restore a lot
OL,13,Fof people's faith, not only in the
OL,14,FLabour Party, but in politics as a
OL,15,Fwhole."
OL,17,FThe King of the North
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
