OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FThere are hidden benefits as well.
OL,7,FKieran described the scene as
OL,8,F"surreal," telling ITV News: "The
OL,9,Fother day I got interviewed by the
OL,10,FGuardian for a podcast.
OL,12,F"I went back home, went out to the
OL,13,Fshops again with my wife, and we got
OL,14,Finterviewed by a Japanese journalist.
OL,15,FYou can't move for journalists at the
OL,16,Fmoment.
OL,18,F"But then equally, I saw one in the
OL,19,Fpub the other day, so you're spending
OL,20,Fmoney locally, so that's okay."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
