OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,F"The only simple thing we saw was an
OL,7,Falmost universal dislike of Keir
OL,8,FStarmer," said Co-founder of JL
OL,9,FPartners Tom Lubbock.
OL,11,FA note on the focus group
OL,13,FITV News spoke to a focus group in
OL,14,FMakerfield put together by JL
OL,15,FPartners, ahead of the byelection on
OL,16,FJune 18.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G29/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
