FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30530
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FThe group consisted of eight
OL,7,Fparticipants, four of whom said they
OL,8,Fbacked Labour, three who supported
OL,9,FReform and one backing Rupert Lowe's
OL,10,FRestore Britain Party.
OL,12,FCo-founder of JL Partners, Tom
OL,13,FLubbock, who was commissioned by
OL,14,Fcampaign group 38 Degrees to put
OL,15,Ftogether this focus group, spoke with
OL,16,FRobert Peston after the meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G30/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
