OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781302284
OL,3,CWhat do voters in the UK's most
OL,4,Cconsequential byelection really think?
OL,6,FHe described next week's byelection as
OL,7,F"the most important in a generation,"
OL,8,Fsaying of the themes discussed in the
OL,9,Ffocus group: "The only simple thing we
OL,10,Fsaw was an almost universal dislike of
OL,11,FKeir Starmer."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FVoters in Makerfield will cast their
OL,19,Fballots on June 18, with results
OL,20,Fexpected in the early hours of the
OL,21,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G31/32
